<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', {
    pageTitle: pageTitle,
    pageDescription: pageDescription,
    canonicalUrl,
    canonicalPath,
    ogImage,
    structuredData,
    pageScripts: ['/backend.js']
  }) %>
</head>
<body class="page">
  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <main class="page-main">
    <section class="page-hero shell">
      <p class="eyebrow">Weekly subscription</p>
      <h1>Build the easiest health habit in your week.</h1>
      <p class="lede">Our weekly microgreen subscription Kerala plan is built for households in Pattambi, Valanchery, Pallipuram, and Pulamanthole that want fresher greens without extra shopping friction.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section section--tint">
      <div class="shell feature-split">
        <div class="feature-copy">
          <div class="section-heading section-heading--compact">
            <h2>Why start with a weekly box?</h2>
            <p>A subscription keeps fresh greens visible in the fridge, which is what turns good intentions into actual daily use.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="stack-list">
            <article class="content-row reveal-on-scroll">
              <h3>Harvested close to delivery</h3>
              <p>The whole model exists to keep the freshness window short across the Pattambi delivery belt.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="content-row reveal-on-scroll">
              <h3>Easy to use in Kerala meals</h3>
              <p>Use the trays with breakfast, lunch, curries, rice bowls, juices, and simple evening plates.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="content-row reveal-on-scroll">
              <h3>WhatsApp-first support</h3>
              <p>Message in Malayalam or English if you want help choosing trays or confirming the right area.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-card subscribe-card">
          <h2>Get updates or order now</h2>
          <p class="small-note">Join the email list for weekly harvest updates, or skip straight to WhatsApp if you are ready.</p>

          <%- include('partials/newsletter-form', {
            source: 'subscribe-page',
            submitLabel: 'Join the weekly list',
            showFirstName: true,
            showFeedback: true
          }) %>

          <div class="stacked-cta">
            <a class="button button-primary button-block" href="<%= site.whatsappHref %>">Order on WhatsApp</a>
            <a class="button button-secondary button-block" href="/shop">Shop one-time boxes</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
